tle=\"Members\">Members</a></th><td colspan=\"13\">Yes</td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"7\"><a href=\"/w/Quest_items\" title=\"Quest items\">Quest item</a></th><td colspan=\"13\">No</td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"20\" class=\"infobox-padding\"></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"20\" class=\"infobox-subheader\">Properties</th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"20\" class=\"infobox-padding\"></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"7\"><a href=\"/w/Items#Tradeability\" title=\"Items\">Tradeable</a></th><td colspan=\"13\">Yes</td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"7\"><a href=\"/w/Worn_Equipment\" title=\"Worn Equipment\">Equipable</a></th><td colspan=\"13\">No</td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"7\"><a href=\"/w/Stackable_items\" title=\"Stackable items\">Stackable</a></th><td colspan=\"13\">No</td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"7\"><a href=\"/w/Note\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Note\">Noteable</a></th><td colspan=\"13\">Yes</td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"7\"><a href=\"/w/Choose_Option\" title=\"Choose Option\">Options</a></th><td colspan=\"13\">Read</td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"7\"><a href=\"/w/Destroy\" title=\"Destroy\">Destroy</a></th><td colspan=\"13\">Drop</td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"7\"><a href=\"/w/Examine\" title=\"Examine\">Examine</a></th><td colspan=\"13\">A book on elven crystal.</td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"20\" class=\"infobox-padding\"></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"20\" class=\"infobox-subheader\">Values</th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"20\" class=\"infobox-padding\"></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"7\"><a href=\"/w/Value\" title=\"Value\">Value</a></th><td colspan=\"13\">2 coins</td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"7\"><a href=\"/w/High_Level_Alchemy\" title=\"High Level Alchemy\">High alch</a></th><td colspan=\"13\">1 coin</td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"7\"><a href=\"/w/Low_Level_Alchemy\" title=\"Low Level Alchemy\">Low alch</a></th><td colspan=\"13\">0 coins</td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"7\"><a href=\"/w/Weight\" title=\"Weight\">Weight</a></th><td colspan=\"13\">0.51 kg</td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"20\" class=\"infobox-padding\"></td></tr><tr class=\"advanced-data\"><th colspan=\"20\" class=\"infobox-subheader\">Advanced data</th></tr><tr class=\"advanced-data\"><td colspan=\"20\" class=\"infobox-padding\"></td></tr><tr class=\"advanced-data\"><th colspan=\"7\">Item ID</th><td colspan=\"13\">4313</td></tr><tr class=\"advanced-data\"><td colspan=\"20\" class=\"infobox-padding\"></td></tr></tbody></table><div class=\"infobox-smw-data\" style=\"display:none\"></div>\n<div class=\"floatleft\"><a href=\"/w/File:Crystal_singing_for_beginners_detail.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Crystal singing for beginners detail.png\" src=\"/images/thumb/Crystal_singing_for_beginners_detail.png/130px-Crystal_singing_for_beginners_detail.png?2315b\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"130\" height=\"121\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/Crystal_singing_for_beginners_detail.png/195px-Crystal_singing_for_beginners_detail.png?2315b 1.5x, /images/thumb/Crystal_singing_for_beginners_detail.png/260px-Crystal_singing_for_beginners_detail.png?2315b 2x\" data-file-width=\"1439\" data-file-height=\"1342\" /></a></div>\n<p><b>Crystal singing for beginners</b> is a book given to the player by <a href=\"/w/Ilfeen\" title=\"Ilfeen\">Ilfeen</a> after talking to her after completing the <a href=\"/w/Roving_Elves\" title=\"Roving Elves\">Roving Elves</a> quest.\n</p><p>Besides appearances, it contains the same contents to <i>Crystal Singing for Beginners (trans. Oaknock)</i> - <a href=\"/w/A_handwritten_book\" title=\"A handwritten book\">A handwritten book</a>. This book can then be found in the bookcase of a <a href=\"/w/Player-owned_house\" title=\"Player-owned house\">player-owned house</a> or in the <a href=\"/w/Grand_Library\" title=\"Grand Library\">Grand Library</a> in <a href=\"/w/Prifddinas\" title=\"Prifddinas\">Prifddinas</a> after completion of <a href=\"/w/Song_of_the_Elves\" title=\"Song of the Elves\">Song of the Elves</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Transcript\">Transcript</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/Crystal_singing_for_beginners?section=1&amp;veaction=edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" title=\"Edit section: Transcript\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-divider\"> | </span><a href=\"/w/Crystal_singing_for_beginners?action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Transcript\">edit source</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div><div class=\"seealso\">The following text is transcluded from <a href=\"/w/Transcript:Crystal_singing_for_beginners\" title=\"Transcript:Crystal singing for beginners\">Transcript:Crystal singing for beginners</a>.</div><div class=\"transcript\">\n<div style=\"font-weight:bold;padding-top:10px;font-size:17px\">Chapter 1: Crystal Seed</div><hr />\n<p>As you may know, all crystal equipment is grown from a crystal seed. You may not know that all crystal seeds come from the same place; Tarddiad, the ancestral homeworld of the elves.\n</p><p>Reading the 'Cerddi' tells us that crystal seeds are sentient, although no one has ever been able converse with any crystal consciousness other than that of Seren herself.\n</p><p>One of the ways we can see this consciousness in action is in the way that crystal equipment, when first used, becomes aligned to that person.\n</p>\n<div style=\"font-weight:bold;padding-top:10px;font-size:17px\">Chapter 2: Crystal Chanting</div><hr />\n<p>As far as we can tell there have always been those with the ability to chant crystal, these tend to be from the Ithell clan, but it has been known for these 'Crystal Chanters' to be born to other clans as well.\n</p><p>The thing that makes 'Crystal Chanters' special is their ability to vocalise perfect pitches.\n</p><p>The idea behind chanting is quite simple: different pitches can change the shape and size of any facet of the seed. This allows a practiced chanter to make any number of shapes.\n</p><p>It is also possible for particularly gifted individuals to imbue powers into these objects. The only problem with this process is that it is very costly and time consuming.\n</p><p>The process can, however, be made more economical: the better the chanter knows the person for whom they are creating items, the easier it is to make.\n</p>\n<div style=\"font-weight:bold;padding-top:10px;font-size:17px\">Chapter 3: Crystal Properties</div><hr />\n<p>Although crystal seeds are highly convenient, they do have some drawbacks, the foremost of these is their brittleness.\n</p><p>This means that crystal equipment will eventually revert back to its original form, that of the crystal seed. However, crystal seeds can be reused to create new crystal equipment. Some equipment can also be reinforced to slow degradation.\n</p>\nCrystal seeds are among our most valuable assets, but with us unable to return to our homeworld since the loss of the World Gate, access to this resource has been lost. Luckily, there is no known way to fully destroy a crystal seed.</div></div>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Changes\">Changes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/Crystal_singing_for_beginners?section=2&amp;veaction=edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" title=\"Edit section: Changes\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-divider\"> | </span><a href=\"/w/Crystal_singing_for_beginners?action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: Changes\">edit source</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<table class=\"wikitable mw-collapsible sortable\" style=\"max-width:800px\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<th>Date\n</th>\n<th class=\"unsortable\">Changes\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<td data-sort-value=\"25 July 2019\"><a href=\"/w/25_July\" title=\"25 July\">25&#160;July</a>&#160;<a href=\"/w/2019\" title=\"2019\">2019</a><br />(<a href=\"/w/Update:Song_of_the_Elves\" title=\"Update:Song of the Elves\">update</a>)\n</td>\n<td>\n<ul><li>The item's name was changed from \"Crystal of seren\" to \"Crystal singing for beginners\".</li>\n<li>Some text was modified to be consistent with the elven lore of both <i>RuneScape</i> and <i>Old School RuneScape</i>.</li></ul>\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<table class=\"navbox nowraplinks mw-collapsible\" data-expandtext=\"show\" data-navbox-name=\"Roving Elves\" data-collapsetext=\"hide\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" class=\"navbox-title\" id=\"navbox-title\"><div class=\"navbox-title-name-notplain\"><div class=\"navbar\" style=\"float:left;text-align:left;width:6em\"><div class=\"plainlinks noprint\" style=\"background-color:transparent;padding:0;font-weight:normal;font-size:xx-small;white-space:nowrap\"><a href=\"/w/Template:Roving_Elves\" title=\"Template:Roving Elves\"><span title=\"View this template\">v</span></a>&#160;<span style=\"font-size:80%\">&#8226;</span>&#160;<a class=\"text\" href=\"https://oldschool.runescape.wiki/w/Template_talk:Roving_Elves\"><span title=\"Discussion about this template\">d</span></a>&#160;<span style=\"font-size:80%\">&#8226;</span>&#160;<a class=\"text\" href=\"https://oldschool.runescape.wiki/w/Template:Roving_Elves?action=edit\"><span title=\"Edit this template\">e</span></a></div></div><span><a href=\"/w/Roving_Elves\" title=\"Roving Elves\">Roving Elves</a></span></div></th></tr><tr class=\"navbox-group\"><td class=\"navbox-group-title\">NPCs</td><td class=\"navbox-list\">\n<ul><li><span class=\"plink-template\"><a href=\"/w/Islwyn\" title=\"Islwyn\"><img alt=\"Islwyn chathead.png: Chat head image of Islwyn\" src=\"/images/thumb/Islwyn_chathead.png/30px-Islwyn_chathead.png?9ca9c\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"30\" height=\"35\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/Islwyn_chathead.png/45px-Islwyn_chathead.png?9ca9c 1.5x, /images/thumb/Islwyn_chathead.png/59px-Islwyn_chathead.png?9ca9c 2x\" data-file-width=\"79\" data-file-height=\"93\" /></a></span><a href=\"/w/Islwyn\" title=\"Islwyn\">Islwyn</a></li>\n<li><span class=\"plink-template\"><a href=\"/w/Eluned\" title=\"Eluned\"><img alt=\"Eluned chathead.png: Chat head image of Elu